    .string "Caption$"
    .string "A young boy who lives in Hyrule. He is\n"
    .string "close friends with Princess Zelda.$"
    .string "A young boy on a quest with Ezlo to\n"
    .string "restore the Four Sword.\n"
    .string "With the sword's power, he hopes to\n"
    .string "remove the curse on Princess Zelda.$"
    .string "A bright and cheery princess from\n"
    .string "Hyrule's royal family.\n"
    .string "She loves to sneak out of the castle\n"
    .string "to visit her good friend, {PLAYER}.$"
    .string "A strange creature that looks at first\n"
    .string "like a cap. He speaks roughly and\n"
    .string "treats {PLAYER} like a child, but he\n"
    .string "actually really likes {PLAYER}.$"
    .string "When the young Minish donned Ezlo's\n"
    .string "magic cap, he took this evil form. Now,\n"
    .string "he searches for the light force in his\n"
    .string "quest to become all-powerful.$"
    .string "The king of Hyrule. Reported to have\n"
    .string "been a fine swordsman, he appeared in\n"
    .string "the Picori Festival tournament as a\n"
    .string "youth and fought to a draw with Smith.$"
    .string "The supporting pillar of Hyrule. He\n"
    .string "is also in charge of Princess Zelda's\n"
    .string "education, so when she goes missing,\n"
    .string "he gets frustrated.$"
    .string "The finest swordsmith in Hyrule. As a\n"
    .string "young man, he was a great swordsman.\n"
    .string "He and King Daltus are friends and\n"
    .string "enjoyed a pleasant rivalry as youths.$"
    .string "The mayor of the town of Hyrule. He's a\n"
    .string "big collector of odd masks. He's built a\n"
    .string "shelter into his garden just in case\n"
    .string "monsters ever attack Hyrule.$"
    .string "Second in command at Hyrule's post\n"
    .string "office. She's mellow and laid-back,\n"
    .string "entirely unlike the high-strung and\n"
    .string "easily excitable Stamp.$"
    .string "A busy, hardworking postal employee,\n"
    .string "although he can be a touch edgy.\n"
    .string "The stamp he uses is his own personal\n"
    .string "one, so please don't borrow it. Thanks.$"
    .string "The proprietor of {COLOR}{YELLOW}Rem's Shoe Store{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "Using his {QT}secret technique,{QT} he makes\n"
    .string "shoes in his sleep. Princess Zelda is\n"
    .string "his single biggest source of income.$"
    .string "A gruff-talking academic type who is\n"
    .string "obsessed with studying the Picori.\n"
    .string "He doesn't seem to be aware that they\n"
    .string "are actually living in his own house.$"
    .string "A sculptor of finely crafted {COLOR}{YELLOW}figurines{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "Many consider him the best sculptor\n"
    .string "in all of Hyrule. He enjoys collecting\n"
    .string "{COLOR}{YELLOW}Mysterious Shells{COLOR}{WHITE}.$"
    .string "Owner of the {COLOR}{YELLOW}Chest Mini-Game Shop{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "Carlov's younger brother. He detests\n"
    .string "gambling, but he has made the biggest\n"
    .string "gamble of all: entrepreneurship.$"
    .string "The handy neighborhood gear seller,\n"
    .string "also called {COLOR}{YELLOW}Stockwell the Well-Stocked{COLOR}{WHITE}.\n"
    .string "He complains that he's been too busy\n"
    .string "lately to see his dog, Fifi.$"
    .string "His mysterious {COLOR}{YELLOW}dungeon-simulation\n"
    .string "game{COLOR}{WHITE} is very popular in Hyrule. It gives\n"
    .string "players the illusion of fighting real\n"
    .string "monsters in real dungeons.$"
    .string "He wants to rent out his house in town,\n"
    .string "but he's too overbearing to attract\n"
    .string "a tenant. He doesn't even seem to\n"
    .string "realize what the problem is...$"
    .string "This young woman tends to her cuccos\n"
    .string "in Hyrule Town.\n"
    .string "If you help her gather her loose\n"
    .string "cuccos, she'll give you a reward.$"
    .string "Hyrule's vegetable vendor. He sells fine\n"
    .string "produce. He also argues constantly\n"
    .string "with the fruit vendor, Pina, over\n"
    .string "the health benefits of vegetables.$"
    .string "Hyrule's fruit vendor. She hates\n"
    .string "vegetables, so she won't even sell\n"
    .string "tomatoes, even though they\n"
    .string "technically ARE fruits. Freak.$"
    .string "Though he is an adult, he is very good\n"
    .string "at finding Picolyte made by the Minish.\n"
    .string "And he is very, VERY convincing about\n"
    .string "their healthful properties.$"
    .string "A very serious mail deliveryman.\n"
    .string "He continues to make every delivery\n"
    .string "right on time every day.$"
    .string "A hermit who lives on Mount Crenel.\n"
    .string "He has lots of Kinstone pieces.\n"
    .string "He brags that he won the festival \n"
    .string "tournament when he was younger.$"
    .string "A weird old lady living in Percy's\n"
    .string "house without his permission.\n"
    .string "She doesn't want you to turn on the\n"
    .string "lights. She might actually be a...$"
    .string "The gravedigger at the cemetery.\n"
    .string "They say he has the power to speak\n"
    .string "with the dead. He fuses the Kinstones\n"
    .string "he digs up with the local ghosts.$"
    .string "The spirit of an ancient king of Hyrule\n"
    .string "who wishes to secure peace in his land\n"
    .string "from beyond the grave. He was very\n"
    .string "fond of the people of the Wind Tribe.$"
    .string "A wizard who lives in the Minish Woods.\n"
    .string "She sells magic items with odd powers.\n"
    .string "She's looking for an apprentice to whom\n"
    .string "she can teach her mystic spells.$"
    .string "The Great Butterfly Fairy of Minish\n"
    .string "Woods. She provides you with a\n"
    .string "larger wallet, allowing you to carry\n"
    .string "more Rupees with you.$"
    .string "The Great Mayfly Fairy of Mount\n"
    .string "Crenel. She provides you with a larger\n"
    .string "bomb bag, allowing you to carry more\n"
    .string "bombs with you.$"
    .string "The Great Dragonfly Fairy of Royal\n"
    .string "Valley. She gives you a larger\n"
    .string "quiver, allowing you to carry\n"
    .string "more arrows with you.$"
    .string "A poet who lives in Western Wood.\n"
    .string "He comes home from a long journey to\n"
    .string "find his house occupied by an unwanted\n"
    .string "guest. Poor guy...$"
    .string "She's looking for a house in Hyrule\n"
    .string "to move into. She is descended from\n"
    .string "a line of oracles in the land of\n"
    .string "Labrynna.$"
    .string "She's looking for a house in Hyrule to\n"
    .string "move into. She's a very helpful person,\n"
    .string "but people take advantage of her kind\n"
    .string "nature. This really bothers her.$"
    .string "She's looking for a house in Hyrule to\n"
    .string "move into. She is a famous dancer from\n"
    .string "the land of Holodrum.$"
    .string "A rare butterfly said to bring\n"
    .string "happiness to those who catch it.\n"
    .string "If you see one on your journeys,\n"
    .string "try to grab it!$"
    .string "A strange Ghini who wants to fuse\n"
    .string "Kinstone pieces, which is somewhat\n"
    .string "peculiar for a monster. She has a lot\n"
    .string "of pieces, so keep on fusing!$"
    .string "A Minish living in Minish Village. He\n"
    .string "speaks some human languages. He sees\n"
    .string "that {PLAYER} is human with one look.\n"
    .string "He's "
